OL,3,CWhy this tattoo could get athletes
OL,4,Cbanned from the Paralympics
OL,6,FThe 2024 Olympics are over, and with
OL,7,Fthat, attentions now shift towards the
OL,8,FParis Paralympic Games which will kick-
OL,9,Foff in just over a week.
OL,11,FParalympic athletes will be entering
OL,12,Fthe last stage of their preparations
OL,13,Fahead of the Games, but one little-
OL,14,Fknown rule could stop some of them
OL,15,Fcompeting altogether.
OL,17,FIt has become a rite of passage for
OL,18,FOlympians to get a tattoo of the
OL,19,Ficonic rings, forever commemorating
OL,20,Ftheir performance and participation.
