OL,3,CWhy this tattoo could get athletes
OL,4,Cbanned from the Paralympics
OL,6,FHowever, for Paralympians, those
OL,7,Fdisplaying the five rings could be
OL,8,Fpunished if they fail to cover up
OL,9,Ftheir body art.
OL,11,FRetired Paralympian Josef Craig was on
OL,12,Fthe receiving end of this obscure rule
OL,13,Fahead of the 2016 Rio Paralympic Games
OL,14,Fwhen he was penalised for showing the
OL,15,Frings tattoo on his chest.
OL,17,FThe British swimmer was competing in
OL,18,Fthe IPC Swimming European
OL,19,FChampionships and won his heat in the
OL,20,FS8 100m freestyle competition.
