OL,3,CWhy this tattoo could get athletes
OL,4,Cbanned from the Paralympics
OL,6,FBut, despite his performance in the
OL,7,Fpool, the 27-year-old who has cerebral
OL,8,Fpalsy was disqualified.
OL,10,FWhy the difference in rules between
OL,11,Fthe Olympics and Paralympics?
OL,13,FThe difference in rules comes down to
OL,14,Fboth Games having a different
OL,15,Fgoverning body.
OL,17,FThe International Paralympic Committee
OL,18,F(IPC) forbids athletes from "body
OL,19,Fadvertising", with the iconic rings
OL,20,Ffalling under that purview.
