OL,3,CWhy this tattoo could get athletes
OL,4,Cbanned from the Paralympics
OL,6,FEssentially the Olympic rings are just
OL,7,Fthat, the logo of the Olympics and not
OL,8,Fthat of the Paralympics.
OL,10,FThe Paralympics has its own symbol,
OL,11,Fthe Agitos logo, which can be shown by
OL,12,Fathletes.
OL,14,FThe International Olympic Committee
OL,15,F(IOC) forbids athletes from showcasing
OL,16,Ftattoos that advertise a product.
OL,18,FAt the time of his disqualification,
OL,19,Fthe IPC said: "Body advertising is not
OL,20,Fallowed in any way whatsoever and that
OL,21,Fincludes the Olympic rings."
